text: Prikubansky () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Takhtamukayskoye Rural Settlement of Takhtamukaysky District, the Republic of Adygea, Russia. The population was 1126 as of 2018. There are 9 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Takhtamukaysky District
title: Prikubansky, Republic of Adygea
